# Keep the build context small and prevent host-platform artifacts
# (node_modules, .next, dist) from being copied over the in-container
# install/build output.

**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/.git
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
**/*.log

# Env files (never needed inside the build context)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Docs / misc
dev_docs/
docs/
*.md
